&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Consultant Ophthalmologist with a special interest in Glaucoma&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applicants are invited to apply for Consultant Ophthalmologist post based at the Hillingdon Hospital and Mount Vernon Hospital sites. It will predominantly cover the Glaucoma Service complement the provision of Ophthalmology services. They will also be expected to support Hillingdon patients treated at the Western Eye Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post is substantive . This is an exciting time for the unit and the successful candidate will need to show enthusiasm and interest in developing the specialist Ophthalmology Services in secondary and community care&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Informal discussions regarding this post would be welcomed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please contact Ms Sheena George/ Prof Bloom in the first instance on 01895 279699 Sheena.George@nhs.net /&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;p.bloom@nhs.net&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
